Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,HADORRA'S CHALLENGE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran... falls!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An Aban Strash?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that... the Hero brat?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-How can there be this many\Npeople out there stronger than me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn... it all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never drawn my sword\Nwithout thinking before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt my sword's will\Nand my own will as one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I completely forgot about the seal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I could think about was saving...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's your sword.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impressive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With our blades, not even\Nthe Dark Citadel Gate will hold.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go, Dai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Focus all of your strength into this blow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This rumbling...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They breached it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That gate that was sealed\Nby the Dark King's power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Send for another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:03:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my king.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We did it! The entrance\Nto Ban Palace is open!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were bound to succeed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The combined might of two Dragon Knights\Nis a force that normally should not exist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shattering the gate is not our goal.\NKeep your guard up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come! Our target is Dark King Ban!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This shaking can only mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai and Baran have breached\Nthe Dark Citadel Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fenbren is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where are you going, Hym?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To avenge Fenbren!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten, Hym,\Nyour vow to Lord Hadorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With Fenbren's insubordination,\Nhow can we abandon our position now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Our purpose here is to allow Lord Hadorra\Nto fight Dai and Baran whole-heartedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra intends to fight Dai and Baran,\Ntwo Dragon Knights, at once?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! How is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect. I wouldn't have it\Nany other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick yourselves up. We need to\Ntake them out and follow Dai and Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All that damage and he still shows up\Non the battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he really human?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be immortal. Just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is crazy, Hyunckel.\NYou can barely even stand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That magnificent, reckless fool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, big brute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had just about enough of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, are you sure about this?!\NComing here couldn't have been easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NAll he can do is stand around anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother worrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stand right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Having you stand behind us is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still our senior Disciple of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,just by showing up,\Nyou've given us plenty of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just relax and stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it, but standing still\Nis actually more exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Learn to take a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The bishop's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably. Dai and Baran must have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai and Baran?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they had\Nalready figured out our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra is waiting for Dai and Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He plans to fight two Dragon Knights?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he sure of his victory?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or does he intend to die?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}could it be both?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry!\NFocus on taking them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't the only ones\Nwho can't afford to lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to wipe you all out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's see who gets\Nto go to their leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who will go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some sort of game, Hadorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think us so weak\Nthat you could easily win?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Knights are the ultimate creatures\Ncreated by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing one served under me, Baran,\Nmade me live in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was petrified that you'd come\Nfor my throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when I learned Dai was\Na Dragon Knight, I was terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagined the two of you working together\Nto come and defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that fear has become a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, I find myself looking forward\Nto this fight. Life can be strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He intended to fight both of us\Nfrom the start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fenbren's insubordination was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that inside me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,there was still some lingering\Nnarcissism and desire for glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,These were manifested in Fenbren's\Npersonality through the Forbidden Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Children tend to grow up\Nto be their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I shall defeat Dai, the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And Baran, if you intend to defend Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take both of you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your overconfidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've grown in power somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't assume you can take on\Ntwo Dragon Knights at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall slay you here myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.59,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TWIN SWORD PINNING{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.64,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hadorra isn't being overconfident!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's become a Superior Being!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A Superior Being?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is strong enough\Nto fight both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to fight together!\NIt's the sure way to defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After what he said,\Nyou'd choose to fight him together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you no pride as a Dragon Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could win with just pride, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You already said our target\Nis Dark King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So it begins. The climax of this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Which has the upper hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra may have become quite powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but against Dai and Baran\Nat their full power, he cannot win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Separating from his Royal Guard\Nwas pure suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,he intends to draw out his own power\Nto its limit through desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A clever ploy by Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But, should Hadorra be defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the two Dragons will gain entrance\Ninto the citadel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an impossibility, Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two will never see my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I misjudged you, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you had grown as a warrior...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're still far from ever being\Na true Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If worrying about pride\Nkeeps me from doing what has to be done,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,then I don't want to be\Na true Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm part human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the blood of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always fought for those around me,\Ndoing the best that I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, making sure we defeat Hadorra\Nand Ban is more important than my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up. Who will fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will you both fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight you, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't listen to reason,\Nso I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see in just a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So Dai comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra has a sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, Dai! You've improved\Nsince our last fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai isn't weak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The power of the attacks\Nhe unleashes rivals that of my own!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To fight in place of your father\Nwho has no experience fighting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not as though you know\Nthe extent of my powers either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A weapon in his left hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell's Chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Ionazun!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra has become a formidable enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Dai.\NYou never cease to surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I could say the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He completely nullified my Strash\Nwith his Ionazun spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A wound like that\Nwill regenerate in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it!\NThe Coal of Hell! A Black Core!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How could Dark King Ban\Ndo something so barbaric?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To implant such a thing\Nin his own servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A Black Core?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You had such a thing\Nhidden in Hadorra's body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I said those two will never see my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Hadorra falls,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:17:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,if the Black Core\Nin his body is detonated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,at the very least,\Nwe can bring it to a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A draw? It will blow away\Nthe whole Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, but it won't mean anything\Nto Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fighting\Nin the exterior perimeter after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing's... a bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,An Underworld super-powerful bomb\Ncalled a Black Core.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a nightmare weapon\Nbeyond the definition of a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I once saw one in the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Black Cores are made\Nfrom a stone called Black Crystal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's found deep in the Underworld,\Nand absorbs power endlessly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're weaponized using Old Magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, due to their\Nextreme destructive power,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even evil creatures that casually use\NForbidden Magic fear using Black Cores.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thirteen years ago, when Hadorra rampaged\Nthe surface world as Dark Lord,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fought Veruza, King of the Abyss\Nin the Underworld.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Veruza used a Black Core while battling\Non a certain Underworld Continent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The entire continent was vaporized.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In his attempt to kill me,\Nhe destroyed his own territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Veruza refused to use\Na Black Core after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes sense, considering his ambitions\Nto rule the Underworld and surface world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point\Nif there's nothing left to rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But for Ban to use a Black Core...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems his plan\Nis not to rule the surface world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but to annihilate it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I never intended for Hadorra\Nto be a sacrificial pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I saved him\Nfrom the brink of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I implanted it in him as insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But then he went and\Nturned himself into a Superior Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This was something even I did not expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The power increase beyond his limits\Nhad an adverse effect on the Black Core.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That bomb could be set off at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be manifested in Hadorra\Nas bouts of extreme pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, he assumes it's merely\Ndue to his conversion to a Superior Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing the outcome to a battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is a boring thing indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But we must see it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For my dear right-hand man,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be his final grand performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Awakening as a true warrior\Nultimately shortened your life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How ironic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would prefer that you win and survive...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but should you fall,\Nat least go out in a blaze of glory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be honored to know that your death\Nshall be for the great King Ban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If it explodes, we'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't use spells or Magic Swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight only using blunt force.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible! We can't win like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That Black Core has been imbued\Nwith great Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have absorbed Hadorra's\Nincreased Magic Power to its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply hitting it with a powerful spell\Nmight set it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you both on! Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:18.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:24.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:29.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:35.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:41.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:47.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:53.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:59.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:10.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:16.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:22.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:30.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To avoid setting off the Black Core\Nand alerting Hadorra of its presence,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.65,0:23:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and Baran must\Nhold back their attacks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Hadorra hounds\NDai and Baran relentlessly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.24,0:23:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra gets in position\Nfor his Ultra Combustion Slash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.41,0:23:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Against the overwhelming odds,\NBaran makes a deadly gambit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Hadorra Versus Baran"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
